data.title: Massachusetts teachers to make push for early retirement bill during Wednesday hearing
data.description: Massachusetts teachers on Wednesday will be making the push before the Joint Committee on Public Service for an early retirement bill that would allow educators to purchase years of service or age and districts to usher in a set of new hires.
